....................................................ROLE OF EACH COMPONENTS.........................................

| Component    | Work                   |
| ------------ | ---------------------- |
| Client       | Sends JSON             |
| Controller   | Receives request       |
| @RequestBody | Converts JSON → Object |
| Jackson      | Creates Java object    |
| Service      | Business logic         |
| Repository   | Database communication |
| Hibernate    | Generates SQL          |
| MySQL        | Stores data            |
| Spring Boot  | Manages everything     |

